data.description: Welcome to this inviting ranch-style home, perfectly located within easy reach of the military post, delightful restaurants, trendy shopping, and casino entertainment. This home offers a privacy fenced backyard, three bedrooms, and two well-appointed bathrooms. Step inside to a clean, update-to-date interior featuring a bright kitchen with white cabinets and stainless steel appliances, ready to cater to all your culinary adventures.  Relish in the privacy and comfort of this lovingly maintained residence and make it your own peaceful haven. Your search for the perfect home ends here!
